OL,3,CWhy is voter turnout so low in the
OL,4,CScottish Parliament election?
OL,6,FOne of the first things we find out at
OL,7,Fany election count is turnout - how
OL,8,Fmany people who were registered to
OL,9,Fvote actually did so.
OL,11,FAnd across the board in the South of
OL,12,FScotland, it's down quite considerably.
OL,14,FThat could be for a number of reasons.
OL,15,FYou might have heard it referred to as
OL,16,F'the scunner factor' - where voters
OL,17,Fare so disenchanted with the
OL,18,Fcandidates on offer, they don't think
OL,19,Fit's worth voting at all.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/4
