OL,3,CWhy is voter turnout so low in the
OL,4,CScottish Parliament election?
OL,6,FIt's been a somewhat negative
OL,7,Fcampaign, with most parties asking
OL,8,Fpeople for their votes to stop another
OL,9,Fparty from gaining - or retaining -
OL,10,Fpower.
OL,12,FAnd there seems to have been a dearth
OL,13,Fof standout policies from any of the
OL,14,Fparties, with very few big ideas that
OL,15,Fpeople can get behind.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/4
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
