OL,3,CWhy is voter turnout so low in the
OL,4,CScottish Parliament election?
OL,6,FIt's seems especially pertinent in
OL,7,FEttrick, Roxburgh and Berwickshire.
OL,8,FAhead of this election, it was
OL,9,Fconsidered the safest seat in the
OL,10,Fcountry for the Conservatives - so is
OL,11,Fthere any wonder people didn't think
OL,12,Ftheir vote mattered?
OL,14,FMeanwhile, a massive 42 MSPs are
OL,15,Fstanding down in this election - big
OL,16,Fnames, like Nicola Sturgeon, Douglas
OL,17,FRoss and Kate Forbes just some of them.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/4
