OL,3,CWhy is voter turnout so low in the
OL,4,CScottish Parliament election?
OL,6,FThe former MSP for Midlothian South,
OL,7,FTweeddale and Lauderdale, Christine
OL,8,FGrahame, is among those who aren't
OL,9,Fseeking a return to Holyrood after
OL,10,Fover two decades.
OL,12,FWith such a loss of heavy hitters and
OL,13,Fnames the electorate has become
OL,14,Faccustomed to, it may be that the new
OL,15,Fcrop of candidates just haven't been
OL,16,Fable to cut though at the ballot box.
OL,18,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,19,Four political experts are across all
OL,20,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,21,Fto the latest episode below...
